raw_data.risk_item: Jiangsu Province Hospital of Chinese Medicine
raw_data.finding_summary: On February 22, 2022, Jiangsu Province Hospital of Chinese Medicine (also known as the Affiliated Hospital of Nanjing University of Chinese Medicine) signed a cooperation agreement with Nanjing University. This agreement aims to explore new models of university-hospital collaboration, strengthening cooperation in areas such as talent training, education and training, and scientific research [1].
